sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store Service<br/>80/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    participant Redis as Redis/PostgreSQL<br/>6379/5432 TCP<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    participant Registry as Registry Service<br/>80/443 TCP gRPC/REST<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    participant OfflineStore as Offline Store Service<br/>80/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant CronJob as Materialization CronJob

    Note over MLApp,Registry: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval (Real-time Inference)

    MLApp->>Route: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: None/OIDC Bearer Token
    Route->>OnlineStore: Forward Request<br/>TLS1.2+
    OnlineStore->>Registry: GET Feature Metadata<br/>gRPC/REST TLS1.2+ (optional)
    Registry-->>OnlineStore: Feature Schema
    OnlineStore->>Redis: Fetch Pre-computed Features<br/>Password Auth
    Redis-->>OnlineStore: Feature Values
    OnlineStore-->>Route: JSON Response with Features
    Route-->>MLApp: HTTPS 200 OK

    Note over MLApp,S3: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval (Model Training)

    MLApp->>OfflineStore: POST /get-historical-features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS1.2+ (optional)<br/>Auth: None/OIDC/RBAC
    OfflineStore->>Registry: GET Feature Definitions<br/>gRPC/REST
    Registry-->>OfflineStore: Feature Metadata
    OfflineStore->>S3: Fetch Historical Parquet Files<br/>AWS IAM/Service Account
    S3-->>OfflineStore: Parquet Data
    OfflineStore-->>MLApp: Historical Feature DataFrame

    Note over CronJob,Redis: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Scheduled)

    CronJob->>OfflineStore: Fetch Latest Features<br/>Service Account Token
    OfflineStore->>S3: Read Raw Data<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>OfflineStore: Raw Feature Data
    OfflineStore-->>CronJob: Computed Features
    CronJob->>OnlineStore: Write Features<br/>Service Account Token
    OnlineStore->>Redis: Store Pre-computed Features<br/>Password Auth
    Redis-->>OnlineStore: Write Confirmation
